OL,3,CDomestic abuse survivors say #500
OL,4,Cgovernment flee fund doesn't go far
OL,5,Cenough
OL,7,FBy Anna Georgevic, Producer
OL,9,FDomestic abuse survivors in England
OL,10,Fand Wales will be able to apply for a
OL,11,Fone-off payment of up to #500 in a new
OL,12,Finitiative launched by the Home Office
OL,13,Fand Women's Aid from Wednesday.
OL,15,FThe will help victims of domestic
OL,16,Fviolence escape a violent partner or
OL,17,Fhelp support them so they do not have
OL,18,Fto return to an abusive relationship.
