OL,5,Cenough
OL,7,FThe #2 million scheme builds on
OL,8,Fsuccessful pilot scheme last year,
OL,9,Fwhich helped more than 600 vulnerable
OL,10,Fwomen find safety.
OL,12,FWomen's Aid CEO Farah Nazeer welcomed
OL,13,Fthe new flee fund along with a future
OL,14,Ffund of up to #2,500 per individual.
OL,15,FHowever, she said: "What the fund
OL,16,Fdoesn't do, and what it will never do,
OL,17,Fis compensate for the gaps that
OL,18,Fsurvivors face that make the funds
OL,19,Fnecessary in the first place."
