OL,7,FShe told ITV News: "We don't want
OL,8,Fsilver bullets anymore. What we want
OL,9,Fis a whole system response. So
OL,10,Fultimately, we don't need sticking
OL,11,Fplasters."
OL,13,FSome survivors also believe the new
OL,14,Ffunding doesn't go far enough.
OL,16,FLisa* who fled from her abusive
OL,17,Fpartner during lockdown says: "For me,
OL,18,Ffive hundred pounds is going nowhere.
OL,19,FIt's all well and good if you don't
OL,20,Freally have a lot to pay for, but it
OL,21,Fwould never be enough."
