OL,7,FIn 2021, when faced with life
OL,8,Fthreatening conditions, Lisa managed
OL,9,Fto escape to the charity, . Being
OL,10,Fstalked by him, she says, "was like
OL,11,Fbeing a prisoner".
OL,13,FLisa had to travel some distance to
OL,14,Fmove as far away as possible from her
OL,15,Fperpetrator. She says fleeing her
OL,16,Fabusive partner cost her nearly #2,000
OL,17,Fand that the new funding for some
OL,18,F"wouldn't even cover the train ticket."
