OL,7,FShe says: "I think this is a good step
OL,8,Fin the right direction to help
OL,9,Fsurvivors I just think that there's
OL,10,Fmore that could be done surrounding
OL,11,Fthis to make it better."
OL,13,FLike Lisa, another survivor of
OL,14,Fdomestic abuse, Rachel Williams, also
OL,15,Fbelieves the flee fund is not enough
OL,16,Fto ensure survivors reach a safe
OL,17,Flocation.
OL,19,FRachel told ITV News, when escaping
OL,20,Fher perpetrator the funding "would not
OL,21,Fhave been the lifeline" she needed.
