OL,8,Ftake into account "how perpetrators
OL,9,Foperate"
OL,11,F"If you're fleeing, it's not just
OL,12,Fabout being in a different house, you
OL,13,Fcan't even stay in the same area
OL,14,Fbecause they will find you, follow you
OL,15,Fand stalk you. The perpetrator will
OL,16,Ffind you in a heartbeat."
