OL,7,FAfter 18 years in an abusive
OL,8,Frelationship, Rachel was shot and
OL,9,Fseverely injured by her violent
OL,10,Fpartner in 2011. He died by suicide.
OL,11,FHer 16-year-old son Jack took his own
OL,12,Flife shortly after the attack on his
OL,13,Fmother. Rachel spent months in
OL,14,Fhospital and now lives with life
OL,15,Faltering injuries.
OL,17,FRachel went on to establish and
OL,18,Fcampaigns tirelessly for victims.
