OL,5,Cenough
OL,7,FHad her former partner not taken his
OL,8,Fown life, she says she would have had
OL,9,Fto leave the country, but argues the
OL,10,Fnew flee fund would not have been
OL,11,Fenough for her to do so.
OL,13,FShe told ITV News: "Say I've accessed
OL,14,Fthis funding, I've got to leave and
OL,15,Fget a flat. I've got to kit the whole
OL,16,Fflat out. I've got put down a month's
OL,17,Fdeposit and rent. What if I want to
OL,18,Fmake it safer with cameras and a ring
OL,19,Fdoorbell? And what do I do next month?
OL,20,FWhere's my food coming from? What is
OL,21,Fthat funding really going to do?"
