OL,7,FRachel also raises concerns over
OL,8,Faccess to the funding.
OL,10,FFrom 31st January 2024, survivors of
OL,11,Fdomestic abuse who do not have the
OL,12,Ffinancial means to leave their abusers
OL,13,Fwill be able to apply for a one-off
OL,14,Fpayment of up to #500 via one of
OL,15,FWomen's Aid's 470 support services.
