OL,7,FHowever, Rachel says: "If the funding
OL,8,Fis in the form of a bank transfer,
OL,9,Fthat's a fierce hurdle and barrier as
OL,10,Fa lot of domestic abuse victims don't
OL,11,Fhave a bank account, so how are they
OL,12,Fgoing to access the funds? And we know
OL,13,Fit's a hassle if it's a joint account
OL,14,Ftrying to kick the perpetrator off the
OL,15,Faccount."
