OL,7,FFunding may also come in the form of a
OL,8,Fvoucher or cash payment. But Rachel
OL,9,Fstresses the practical problems with
OL,10,Fvouchers, as she told ITV News: "Can
OL,11,Fyou imagine going to a landlord, using
OL,12,Fa voucher for a deposit? It's
OL,13,Fabsolutely ridiculous. And are there
OL,14,Fenough places that would even accept
OL,15,Fthese vouchers?"
OL,17,FLike the survivor community, the
OL,18,Fcharity Refuge also believes the
OL,19,Ffunding doesn't go far enough.
