OL,7,FAbigail Ampofo from Refuge says: "This
OL,8,Ffund is only a drop in the ocean
OL,9,Fcompared to what is needed. An extra
OL,10,F#2 million, which is expected to last
OL,11,Funtil March 2025, will barely touch
OL,12,Fthe sides."
OL,14,FRefuge is now calling for funding of
OL,15,F#238 million per year to be allocated
OL,16,Fto domestic abuse services.
