OL,7,FSurvivor Rachel believes the real
OL,8,Fproblem lies in our justice system.
OL,9,FShe says: "Why does a victim have to
OL,10,Fflee? For me, the lifeline would have
OL,11,Fbeen getting the perpetrator and
OL,12,Flocking him up and keeping me safe."
