OL,7,FRetired magistrate Jane* agrees. She
OL,8,Ftold ITV News: "Why aren't the
OL,9,Fperpetrators taken and put somewhere
OL,10,Felse? It's a ludicrous situation and a
OL,11,Fludicrous sticking plaster to give
OL,12,Fsomething that completely needs to be
OL,13,Frethought and challenge the way we
OL,14,Fdeal with perpetrators. The court
OL,15,Fneeds to not fail the victim. The
OL,16,Fcourt needs to stringently deal with
OL,17,Fthose perpetrators."
