OL,7,FJane* is now calling for mandatory
OL,8,Fspecialist training for all
OL,9,Fmagistrates when it comes to dealing
OL,10,Fwith domestic abuse cases.
OL,12,FWomen's Aid CEO Farah Nazeer also
OL,13,Frecognises this issue.
