OL,7,FShe told ITV News: "As we stand, none
OL,8,Fof the systems that wrap around
OL,9,Fsurvivors actually support survivors
OL,10,Fin the way that they deserve and need
OL,11,Fto be supported. The family courts are
OL,12,Fstill not responding to the needs of
OL,13,Fdomestic abuse survivors. Survivors
OL,14,Fare not believed still and they're
OL,15,Fhaving to do horrendous things to try
OL,16,Fand prove their experience."
OL,18,FDespite the new funding, she's calling
OL,19,Ffor systemic change.
