OL,7,FShe said that while she is delighted
OL,8,Fwith the new flee fund: "There's real
OL,9,Fwork that needs to be done to the
OL,10,Fwhole system. There needs to enough
OL,11,Fservices and enough police support in
OL,12,Fthe criminal justice system to support
OL,13,Fand respond to survivors. There's a
OL,14,Fhuge contextual issue here, the
OL,15,Fsystems that support survivors are not
OL,16,Fyet there to support them."
